text: @FedEx You have by far the worst customer support I've ever seen. 3 different calls and 2 different answers on getting a package redelivered. 2nd person sent me straight to voicemail.
@Arithium1 @Arithium1: What about if I did a fantastic job in helping you? Tim, send the tracking # and delivery address and will quickly review. Sonia

@FedExHelp There is absolutely no point, they wont re-deliver it today and wont drop it off at a fedex location so I can pick it up. The driver slapped a door tag on my door and left, no knock or anything as I've been home all day.
@FedExHelp Now if you could have them drop it off at one of the many fedex locations on the way to the main hub that would be helpful.
@Arithium1 @Arithium1: I can still help and would be ideal to get the tracking # please!
